<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kemet Post</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            width: 300px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .image-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .image-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card-content h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card-content ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .card-content ul li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #ff7043;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .btn.close-btn {
            background-color: #ff7043;
        }

        .btn.view-btn {
            background-color: #ff7043;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff5722;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="https://www.base23.com/sites/default/files/kemet.jpg" alt="Kemet Game">
    </div>
    <div class="card-content">
        <h2>KEMET</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>เจ้าของ Post: Account name</li>
            <li>จำนวนสมาชิก: 0/4</li>
            <li>สถานที่: ห้อง หอชาย A</li>
            <li>วันที่: 16/09/2567</li>
            <li>เวลา: 19:00น.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="button-container">
        <button class="btn close-btn">CLOSE</button>
        <button class="btn view-btn">VIEW MEMBER</button>
    </div>
</div>



</body>
</html>
